25
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,560
(Lu Siyan.)

26
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:57,520
(Sudah waktunya kita
tuntaskan dendam ini.)

27
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,900
(Kediaman Lu)

28
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:12,080
Kak Siyan, kau tahu Kabaret Wenrou?

29
