jangan-jangan...

82
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,440
Jangan mendekat.

83
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,440
Jangan.

84
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,000
Teriaklah.

85
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:37,240
Bukankah kau suka berteriak?
Kenapa sekarang diam?

86
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:40,680
Cepat teriak! Teriak tidak?
Kusuruh kau teriak!

87
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:43,040
Jangan sentuh aku, kumohon.

88
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,640
Aku akan menurut, kumohon padamu.

89
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:47,240
Ah!

90
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,880
Perempuan rendahan,
aku akan buat kau menyesal.

91
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:54,240
