121
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:06,000
Bunga itu sulit dirawat,
jadi cukup langka.

122
00:10:06,920 --> 00:10:09,200
Suatu hari, aku mencium aroma bunga itu

123
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:12,720
