- Panas sekali.

217
00:17:53,365 --> 00:17:54,440
Lin Chuning.

218
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:08,560
Chuning.

219
00:18:10,274 --> 00:18:11,840
Sadarlah.

220
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:15,920
Siyan.

221
00:18:17,080 --> 00:18:20,640
Aku tahu kau tidak nyaman,
aku akan membawamu pulang.

